<div class="text-center">
  <span class="eyebrow">Access</span>
  <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
    The simulation is free. Pro accelerates you.
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    The full simulation is free. Pro is for people who want more depth, faster feedback, and guided accountability.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
    <div class="surface-card p-7">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold">Free Core</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-display text-[var(--color-accent)] font-bold">$0</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs copy-subtle">Full simulation access</p>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm copy-muted">
        <p>✓ Complete team simulation loop (tasks → PRs → review → ship)</p>
        <p>✓ Core lab set with real feedback and quality gates</p>
        <p>✓ Simulated reviewer feedback on every PR</p>
        <p>✓ Delivery record tracking your shipped work</p>
        <p>✓ Self-serve progression at your own pace</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-7 border-[var(--color-accent)]/45">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold">Pro* (Optional)</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-display text-[var(--color-accent)] font-bold">Paid</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs copy-subtle">For faster results and deeper accountability</p>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm copy-muted">
        <p>✓ Advanced multi-step labs and team simulation scenarios</p>
        <p>✓ Deeper, more detailed review feedback</p>
        <p>✓ Curated tracks: frontend delivery, backend, debugging, AI-assisted dev</p>
        <p>✓ Priority support in premium Slack</p>
        <p>✓ Group coaching and Q&A sessions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-6 text-sm copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    Everything you need to practice the team loop is in Free Core. You never hit a paywall to keep learning.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-2 text-xs copy-subtle">*Pro pricing and packaging subject to change. Slack support covers DEVS labs and questions only.</p>

  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="#notify" class="btn-primary cta-glow inline-flex">
      Join early access <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
